<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><meta name="theme-color" content="#07080a"><title>Website Improvement Terminal | Übercorp</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="lab.css?v=1"></head><body><div class="shell"><div class="top"><div class="brand"><span>Ü</span> Übercorp // WEBSITE IMPROVEMENT TERMINAL</div><a class="back" href="../">← CORPORATE HOME</a></div><section class="hero"><p class="eyebrow">PUBLIC ACCESS // QUESTIONABLY AUTHORIZED</p><h1>IMPROVE<br>THE COMPANY.</h1><p>Describe a website change. The algorithm will clone the current Übercorp site into an isolated sandbox, make the requested revision, and let you preview it. Production cannot be changed from this terminal.</p></section><section class="terminal"><div class="bar"><span>SANDBOX GENERATOR</span><span>MAX 5 REVISIONS / HOUR</span></div><div class="body"><form id="labForm"><label for="prompt">TELL ÜBERCORP WHAT IT IS DOING WRONG</label><textarea id="prompt" maxlength="2400" placeholder="Example: Make the history section look like a 1905 pharmaceutical advertisement, but keep the modern navigation."></textarea><div class="actions"><button id="generate" class="primary" type="submit">GENERATE UNAUTHORIZED VERSION</button></div></form><div id="status" class="status">READY // NO PRODUCTION WRITE ACCESS</div><p class="warning">Sandbox output can modify only approved HTML/CSS/JS copies. PHP, server configuration, credentials, GitHub secrets, and production files are outside the model’s allowed output.</p></div><div id="result" class="result"><p class="eyebrow">PROPOSED REVISION</p><h2 id="summary">Sandbox revision</h2><div id="files" class="files"></div><div class="preview-tabs"><button class="active" data-page="index.html">HOME</button><button data-page="citizen.html">CITIZEN</button><button data-page="careers.html">CAREERS</button></div><iframe id="preview" sandbox="allow-scripts" title="Übercorp sandbox preview"></iframe><div class="actions"><button id="submit" class="primary" disabled>SUBMIT TO CENTRAL AUTHORITY</button></div><p class="small">Submission queues the sandbox for review. It does not publish it.</p></div></section></div><script src="lab.js?v=1"></script></body></html>
